text: Facelina zhejiangensis is a species of sea slug, an aeolid nudibranch, a marine gastropod mollusc in the family Facelinidae.MolluscaBase (2018). Facelina zhejiangensis Lin & You, 1990. Accessed on 2018-02-17. ==Distribution== This species has been reported from China. ==References== Category:Facelinidae Category:Gastropods described in 1990
title: Facelina zhejiangensis
